questions.question: A person, who is not looking at object o1, is sitting on and positioned beneath it. Additionally, there is an object o2 classified as food.
questions.dsl: (beneath(o0, o1), not_looking_at(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'), sitting_on(o0, o1)); object(o2, 'food')

questions.question: A person is not looking at object o1. Later, the person is sitting on o1. Finally, the person is holding some food.
questions.dsl: (not_looking_at(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'), object(o2, 'food')); sitting_on(o0, o1); holding(o0, o2)

questions.question: A person is holding the food, not looking at another object o2, while simultaneously touching o2.
questions.dsl: object(o0, 'food'); (holding(o1, o0), not_looking_at(o1, o2), touching(o1, o2)); object(o1, 'person')

questions.question: Initially, a person is touching object o1. Later, the person is not looking at both object o1 and another cup/glass/bottle o2.
questions.dsl: touching(o0, o1); (not_looking_at(o0, o2), not_looking_at(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person')); object(o2, 'cup/glass/bottle')

questions.question: The person is not looking at the chair, and not looking at another object while touching it.
questions.dsl: object(o0, 'chair'); (not_looking_at(o1, o0), not_looking_at(o1, o2), object(o1, 'person'), touching(o1, o2))

questions.question: A person is involved in a sequence where they are not looking at a dish. Subsequently, the person is holding another object o2 and is not looking at it.
questions.dsl: object(o0, 'person'); (not_looking_at(o0, o1), object(o1, 'dish')); (holding(o0, o2), not_looking_at(o0, o2))

questions.question: A person is touching a table. Subsequently, the person is positioned beneath another object o2 and is also sitting on o2.
questions.dsl: (object(o0, 'person'), object(o1, 'table'), touching(o0, o1)); beneath(o0, o2); sitting_on(o0, o2)

questions.question: A person is sitting on object o1 and not looking at it. Later, the person is also not looking at another object o2, which is identified as a cup, glass, or bottle.
questions.dsl: (not_looking_at(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'), sitting_on(o0, o1)); (not_looking_at(o0, o2), object(o2, 'cup/glass/bottle'))

questions.question: A person is beneath and sitting on object o1. Later, the person is not looking at the table.
questions.dsl: (beneath(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'), sitting_on(o0, o1)); object(o2, 'table'); not_looking_at(o0, o2)

questions.question: A person is eating food and is not looking at another object o2. Subsequently, the person is holding object o2.
questions.dsl: (eating(o0, o1), not_looking_at(o0, o2)); (holding(o0, o2), object(o0, 'person'), object(o1, 'food'))
